{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"uf0d5dde2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">简短的回答是：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 可以在</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">主域名相同但子域名不同</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的情况下共享，但无法在</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">完全不同</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的主域名之间直接共享。</span></strong></p><p id=\"u39e1be3c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果想实现跨域共享，需要满足一些严格的条件，并且随着浏览器隐私策略的升级，现在的限制越来越多。下面分情况说明：</span></p><hr id=\"aUF0N\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"BbSJ3\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 同主域下的共享（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h3><p id=\"u3e6a0f90\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最常见的跨子域共享场景。核心是通过设置 Cookie 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性实现。</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uf8fb7733\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">实现方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在设置 Cookie 时，将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性设置为根域名（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，注意开头的点）。这样，该 Cookie 就会被发送到 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 下的所有子域名（包括 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 以及 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 本身）。</span></li><li id=\"u9ffb2d93\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">示例</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"zxDcb\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 后端设置示例（Node.js Express）\nres.cookie('sessionId', 'value', { \n    domain: '.example.com',  // 关键点：设置为根域名\n    path: '/', \n    httpOnly: true \n});</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ud20f1abd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">注意</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：这种方式仅限于共享同一主域名的不同子域，对于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">baidu.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 这种情况无效。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"Azr5B\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 完全跨域共享（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">api.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h3><p id=\"uf44fc91e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是两个完全不同主域名的网站（例如前端在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，后端在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），需要借助 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">CORS（跨域资源共享）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 机制，并配合 Cookie 的现代属性设置。</span></p><p id=\"uc802bcfc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这需要</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">前后端同时配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">才能生效：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u71cfa077\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">后端必须配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ol class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ol ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u3b1e3249\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置明确的允许源</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：响应头 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 不能是通配符 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">*</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，必须是具体的域名（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">https://a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li><li id=\"ue40c6779\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">允许携带凭证</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：设置响应头 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u57594139\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 属性配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：必须设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Secure</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。因为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 要求 Cookie 必须在安全上下文（HTTPS）中才能发送。</span></li></ol></ol><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u88772fbc\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">前端必须配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"xw3Yv\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 前端示例 (使用 fetch)\nfetch('https://api.com/data', {\n    method: 'GET',\n    credentials: 'include' // 关键：告诉浏览器携带目标域名的 Cookie\n});</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub4571233\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在发送请求时，显式设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">withCredentials</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（XHR）或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">credentials: 'include'</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（Fetch API）。</span></li></ul></ul><h3 id=\"eLzVk\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 现代浏览器的限制</span></h3><p id=\"u958a006a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">即使上述代码配置正确，现在实现跨域共享 Cookie 也比以前更难，主要是出于隐私保护：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u71d5ca8c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">第三方 Cookie 限制</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：许多现代浏览器（如 Safari 的 ITP、Chrome 逐步推行的“隐私沙盒”）默认开始限制或完全阻止第三方 Cookie。当你访问 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 时，向 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 发送请求携带的 Cookie 被视为“第三方 Cookie”，可能会被浏览器丢弃。</span></li><li id=\"u9d257e06\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">状态分区</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：Firefox 等浏览器引入了“状态分区”机制。即使你设置了 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，浏览器也可能根据顶级域名对存储进行分区，使得在不同顶级网站下嵌入的同一第三方无法共享之前的 Cookie。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"mM3o0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ua8b19626\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">共享规则</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u80b4e3a1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">完全跨主域</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（如 a.com 和 b.com）：默认</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">不能</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">直接共享，需借助复杂的 CORS 配置和 SameSite=None（但受浏览器第三方 Cookie 策略影响，越来越难）。</span></li><li id=\"u65a734e7\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">子域名间</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（如 a.taobao.com 和 b.taobao.com）：可以通过设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain=.主域名.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 实现共享。</span></li><li id=\"ufd58bcc1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">同一应用不同路径</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：默认可以共享（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Path=/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u05a5578d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">现代最佳实践</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：如果是完全跨域的场景（不同主域名），现在更推荐使用 Token（如 JWT）放在 Authorization Header 中进行认证，而不是依赖 Cookie 共享。这样可以避免第三方 Cookie 限制带来的复杂性和兼容性问题。</span></li></ul></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"uf0d5dde2\" id=\"uf0d5dde2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubf8cd238\" id=\"ubf8cd238\">简短的回答是：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6f595a64\" id=\"u6f595a64\">Cookie 可以在</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u39bda39d\" id=\"u39bda39d\">主域名相同但子域名不同</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u930dd311\" id=\"u930dd311\">的情况下共享，但无法在</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u866860fc\" id=\"u866860fc\">完全不同</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0113269b\" id=\"u0113269b\">的主域名之间直接共享。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u39e1be3c\" id=\"u39e1be3c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf8999d13\" id=\"uf8999d13\">如果想实现跨域共享，需要满足一些严格的条件，并且随着浏览器隐私策略的升级，现在的限制越来越多。下面分情况说明：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22aUF0N%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"BbSJ3\" id=\"BbSJ3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab99c555\" id=\"uab99c555\">1. 同主域下的共享（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u73c407b6\" id=\"u73c407b6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubab8a58c\" id=\"ubab8a58c\">a.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0b530532\" id=\"u0b530532\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua9b5dc34\" id=\"ua9b5dc34\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5ed42148\" id=\"u5ed42148\">b.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9f9cb11a\" id=\"u9f9cb11a\">）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u3e6a0f90\" id=\"u3e6a0f90\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue62dbbf1\" id=\"ue62dbbf1\">这是最常见的跨子域共享场景。核心是通过设置 Cookie 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uec6ccdc7\" id=\"uec6ccdc7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub486e3cf\" id=\"ub486e3cf\">Domain</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u04c3b005\" id=\"u04c3b005\"> 属性实现。</span></p><ul list=\"u1e068298\"><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"uf8fb7733\" id=\"uf8fb7733\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23c5e25b\" id=\"u23c5e25b\">实现方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1735fbb3\" id=\"u1735fbb3\">：在设置 Cookie 时，将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8ce68773\" id=\"u8ce68773\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6983ea57\" id=\"u6983ea57\">Domain</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf265e82\" id=\"ucf265e82\"> 属性设置为根域名（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc7c6c9c7\" id=\"uc7c6c9c7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4ae6006\" id=\"ua4ae6006\">.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue965e72d\" id=\"ue965e72d\">，注意开头的点）。这样，该 Cookie 就会被发送到 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud6bf4afe\" id=\"ud6bf4afe\"><span data-lake-id=\"u264c0b9c\" id=\"u264c0b9c\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc4c22591\" id=\"uc4c22591\"> 下的所有子域名（包括 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u657e7c14\" id=\"u657e7c14\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4f12ef87\" id=\"u4f12ef87\">a.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3b83e2cb\" id=\"u3b83e2cb\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"ua5fc7d64\" id=\"ua5fc7d64\"><span data-lake-id=\"uef448692\" id=\"uef448692\">b.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ubb20ab06\" id=\"ubb20ab06\"> 以及 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u609b6bb3\" id=\"u609b6bb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1640209f\" id=\"u1640209f\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u431ed253\" id=\"u431ed253\"> 本身）。</span></li><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"u9ffb2d93\" id=\"u9ffb2d93\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6611baab\" id=\"u6611baab\">示例</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9e46ad1d\" id=\"u9e46ad1d\">：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88Node.js%20Express%EF%BC%89%5Cnres.cookie('sessionId'%2C%20'value'%2C%20%7B%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20domain%3A%20'.example.com'%2C%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%B9%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%5Cn%20%20%20%20path%3A%20'%2F'%2C%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20httpOnly%3A%20true%20%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22zxDcb%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u1e068298\" start=\"3\"><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"ud20f1abd\" id=\"ud20f1abd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u21658819\" id=\"u21658819\">注意</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0888b374\" id=\"u0888b374\">：这种方式仅限于共享同一主域名的不同子域，对于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7395a142\" id=\"u7395a142\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc4dc7fd\" id=\"ufc4dc7fd\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf3674ccd\" id=\"uf3674ccd\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5ad6cb78\" id=\"u5ad6cb78\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue6db558f\" id=\"ue6db558f\">baidu.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub29f8ea1\" id=\"ub29f8ea1\"> 这种情况无效。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"Azr5B\" id=\"Azr5B\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0b49964a\" id=\"u0b49964a\">2. 完全跨域共享（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u23f04cec\" id=\"u23f04cec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56295c10\" id=\"u56295c10\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2331f2a1\" id=\"u2331f2a1\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ube31707c\" id=\"ube31707c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4ebfc05b\" id=\"u4ebfc05b\">api.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue50b10fa\" id=\"ue50b10fa\">）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uf44fc91e\" id=\"uf44fc91e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u783c9496\" id=\"u783c9496\">如果是两个完全不同主域名的网站（例如前端在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ued206ba6\" id=\"ued206ba6\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf52998d8\" id=\"uf52998d8\">a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u66586576\" id=\"u66586576\">，后端在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0c04754e\" id=\"u0c04754e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56debe2c\" id=\"u56debe2c\">b.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u99b144a8\" id=\"u99b144a8\">），需要借助 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3aa4aa6f\" id=\"u3aa4aa6f\">CORS（跨域资源共享）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udbcf3aac\" id=\"udbcf3aac\"> 机制，并配合 Cookie 的现代属性设置。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc802bcfc\" id=\"uc802bcfc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u64066611\" id=\"u64066611\">这需要</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a363d21\" id=\"u6a363d21\">前后端同时配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98438996\" id=\"u98438996\">才能生效：</span></p><ul list=\"uad007ee2\"><li fid=\"ud25e9cb7\" data-lake-id=\"u71cfa077\" id=\"u71cfa077\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub6e99954\" id=\"ub6e99954\">后端必须配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0d1d8068\" id=\"u0d1d8068\">：</span></li></ul><ol list=\"uad007ee2\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"u3b1e3249\" id=\"u3b1e3249\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9dbf3e7e\" id=\"u9dbf3e7e\">设置明确的允许源</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u78c5dda1\" id=\"u78c5dda1\">：响应头 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8c187a50\" id=\"u8c187a50\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5490f5ed\" id=\"u5490f5ed\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u29f1a825\" id=\"u29f1a825\"> 不能是通配符 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3f09ea4d\" id=\"u3f09ea4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3a1824c\" id=\"ud3a1824c\">*</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5faafb50\" id=\"u5faafb50\">，必须是具体的域名（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1f5c051b\" id=\"u1f5c051b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0b80fda4\" id=\"u0b80fda4\">https://a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf07b9ce0\" id=\"uf07b9ce0\">）。</span></li><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"ue40c6779\" id=\"ue40c6779\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u316ed220\" id=\"u316ed220\">允许携带凭证</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uce6c2b3a\" id=\"uce6c2b3a\">：设置响应头 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3a14855c\" id=\"u3a14855c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uac149f40\" id=\"uac149f40\">Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2211011e\" id=\"u2211011e\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"u57594139\" id=\"u57594139\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u25530482\" id=\"u25530482\">Cookie 属性配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub957f659\" id=\"ub957f659\">：必须设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf14c4879\" id=\"uf14c4879\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue52010fa\" id=\"ue52010fa\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2568d94c\" id=\"u2568d94c\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua21d4fa9\" id=\"ua21d4fa9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u305a175e\" id=\"u305a175e\">Secure</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9595f154\" id=\"u9595f154\">。因为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ucf4d1ebc\" id=\"ucf4d1ebc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d6ffb91\" id=\"u6d6ffb91\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u031263b3\" id=\"u031263b3\"> 要求 Cookie 必须在安全上下文（HTTPS）中才能发送。</span></li></ol><ul list=\"uad007ee2\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"ud25e9cb7\" data-lake-id=\"u88772fbc\" id=\"u88772fbc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u51d03aac\" id=\"u51d03aac\">前端必须配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u68da4b5b\" id=\"u68da4b5b\">：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%20(%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20fetch)%5Cnfetch('https%3A%2F%2Fapi.com%2Fdata'%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20method%3A%20'GET'%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20credentials%3A%20'include'%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%90%BA%E5%B8%A6%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%20Cookie%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22xw3Yv%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"uad007ee2\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u5b58eda0\" data-lake-id=\"ub4571233\" id=\"ub4571233\"><span data-lake-id=\"u937bc4b1\" id=\"u937bc4b1\">在发送请求时，显式设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf3015264\" id=\"uf3015264\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3beb248d\" id=\"u3beb248d\">withCredentials</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u602ba370\" id=\"u602ba370\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uab7356d5\" id=\"uab7356d5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6155b0e5\" id=\"u6155b0e5\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud66a3529\" id=\"ud66a3529\">（XHR）或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uedb8f6a2\" id=\"uedb8f6a2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uadc11745\" id=\"uadc11745\">credentials: 'include'</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua78fb9e5\" id=\"ua78fb9e5\">（Fetch API）。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"eLzVk\" id=\"eLzVk\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0a58ea6d\" id=\"u0a58ea6d\">3. 现代浏览器的限制</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u958a006a\" id=\"u958a006a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u19e553b6\" id=\"u19e553b6\">即使上述代码配置正确，现在实现跨域共享 Cookie 也比以前更难，主要是出于隐私保护：</span></p><ul list=\"u333f4b65\"><li fid=\"ub58f14b8\" data-lake-id=\"u71d5ca8c\" id=\"u71d5ca8c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued0e2feb\" id=\"ued0e2feb\">第三方 Cookie 限制</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u621599fe\" id=\"u621599fe\">：许多现代浏览器（如 Safari 的 ITP、Chrome 逐步推行的“隐私沙盒”）默认开始限制或完全阻止第三方 Cookie。当你访问 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8e5bc991\" id=\"u8e5bc991\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5921053d\" id=\"u5921053d\">a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1e934762\" id=\"u1e934762\"> 时，向 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u40c9bfea\" id=\"u40c9bfea\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud445d585\" id=\"ud445d585\">b.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2288f1a9\" id=\"u2288f1a9\"> 发送请求携带的 Cookie 被视为“第三方 Cookie”，可能会被浏览器丢弃。</span></li><li fid=\"ub58f14b8\" data-lake-id=\"u9d257e06\" id=\"u9d257e06\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u10f7fae0\" id=\"u10f7fae0\">状态分区</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u621320b8\" id=\"u621320b8\">：Firefox 等浏览器引入了“状态分区”机制。即使你设置了 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1ac9801b\" id=\"u1ac9801b\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc5858745\" id=\"uc5858745\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufe4d0118\" id=\"ufe4d0118\">，浏览器也可能根据顶级域名对存储进行分区，使得在不同顶级网站下嵌入的同一第三方无法共享之前的 Cookie。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"mM3o0\" id=\"mM3o0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufef02e18\" id=\"ufef02e18\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"u70914b7e\"><li fid=\"u04fb7b01\" data-lake-id=\"ua8b19626\" id=\"ua8b19626\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf68dc187\" id=\"uf68dc187\">共享规则</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucf9eb4b4\" id=\"ucf9eb4b4\">：</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u70914b7e\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"u80b4e3a1\" id=\"u80b4e3a1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaa23b60d\" id=\"uaa23b60d\">完全跨主域</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6319d117\" id=\"u6319d117\">（如 a.com 和 b.com）：默认</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u81be7e1e\" id=\"u81be7e1e\">不能</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua85e6749\" id=\"ua85e6749\">直接共享，需借助复杂的 CORS 配置和 SameSite=None（但受浏览器第三方 Cookie 策略影响，越来越难）。</span></li><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"u65a734e7\" id=\"u65a734e7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaffe5fef\" id=\"uaffe5fef\">子域名间</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uadc73ee1\" id=\"uadc73ee1\">（如 a.taobao.com 和 b.taobao.com）：可以通过设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc89c0bb3\" id=\"uc89c0bb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8ad82c67\" id=\"u8ad82c67\">Domain=.主域名.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2faf4da6\" id=\"u2faf4da6\"> 实现共享。</span></li><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"ufd58bcc1\" id=\"ufd58bcc1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub824c2cb\" id=\"ub824c2cb\">同一应用不同路径</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3cd95a93\" id=\"u3cd95a93\">：默认可以共享（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u4890a34f\" id=\"u4890a34f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u727b6bc4\" id=\"u727b6bc4\">Path=/</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u283fff67\" id=\"u283fff67\">）。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u70914b7e\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"u04fb7b01\" data-lake-id=\"u05a5578d\" id=\"u05a5578d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2e46b501\" id=\"u2e46b501\">现代最佳实践</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf1e062a2\" id=\"uf1e062a2\">：如果是完全跨域的场景（不同主域名），现在更推荐使用 Token（如 JWT）放在 Authorization Header 中进行认证，而不是依赖 Cookie 共享。这样可以避免第三方 Cookie 限制带来的复杂性和兼容性问题。</span></li></ul>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"uf0d5dde2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">简短的回答是：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 可以在</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">主域名相同但子域名不同</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的情况下共享，但无法在</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">完全不同</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的主域名之间直接共享。</span></strong></p><p id=\"u39e1be3c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果想实现跨域共享，需要满足一些严格的条件，并且随着浏览器隐私策略的升级，现在的限制越来越多。下面分情况说明：</span></p><hr id=\"aUF0N\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"BbSJ3\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 同主域下的共享（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h3><p id=\"u3e6a0f90\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最常见的跨子域共享场景。核心是通过设置 Cookie 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性实现。</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uf8fb7733\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">实现方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在设置 Cookie 时，将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性设置为根域名（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，注意开头的点）。这样，该 Cookie 就会被发送到 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 下的所有子域名（包括 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 以及 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 本身）。</span></li><li id=\"u9ffb2d93\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">示例</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"zxDcb\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 后端设置示例（Node.js Express）\nres.cookie('sessionId', 'value', { \n    domain: '.example.com',  // 关键点：设置为根域名\n    path: '/', \n    httpOnly: true \n});</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ud20f1abd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">注意</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：这种方式仅限于共享同一主域名的不同子域，对于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">baidu.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 这种情况无效。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"Azr5B\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 完全跨域共享（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">example.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">api.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h3><p id=\"uf44fc91e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是两个完全不同主域名的网站（例如前端在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，后端在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），需要借助 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">CORS（跨域资源共享）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 机制，并配合 Cookie 的现代属性设置。</span></p><p id=\"uc802bcfc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这需要</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">前后端同时配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">才能生效：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u71cfa077\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">后端必须配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ol class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ol ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u3b1e3249\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置明确的允许源</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：响应头 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 不能是通配符 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">*</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，必须是具体的域名（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">https://a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li><li id=\"ue40c6779\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">允许携带凭证</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：设置响应头 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u57594139\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 属性配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：必须设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Secure</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。因为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 要求 Cookie 必须在安全上下文（HTTPS）中才能发送。</span></li></ol></ol><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u88772fbc\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">前端必须配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"xw3Yv\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 前端示例 (使用 fetch)\nfetch('https://api.com/data', {\n    method: 'GET',\n    credentials: 'include' // 关键：告诉浏览器携带目标域名的 Cookie\n});</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub4571233\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在发送请求时，显式设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">withCredentials</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（XHR）或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">credentials: 'include'</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（Fetch API）。</span></li></ul></ul><h3 id=\"eLzVk\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 现代浏览器的限制</span></h3><p id=\"u958a006a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">即使上述代码配置正确，现在实现跨域共享 Cookie 也比以前更难，主要是出于隐私保护：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u71d5ca8c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">第三方 Cookie 限制</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：许多现代浏览器（如 Safari 的 ITP、Chrome 逐步推行的“隐私沙盒”）默认开始限制或完全阻止第三方 Cookie。当你访问 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">a.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 时，向 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">b.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 发送请求携带的 Cookie 被视为“第三方 Cookie”，可能会被浏览器丢弃。</span></li><li id=\"u9d257e06\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">状态分区</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：Firefox 等浏览器引入了“状态分区”机制。即使你设置了 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite=None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，浏览器也可能根据顶级域名对存储进行分区，使得在不同顶级网站下嵌入的同一第三方无法共享之前的 Cookie。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"mM3o0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ua8b19626\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">共享规则</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u80b4e3a1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">完全跨主域</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（如 a.com 和 b.com）：默认</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">不能</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">直接共享，需借助复杂的 CORS 配置和 SameSite=None（但受浏览器第三方 Cookie 策略影响，越来越难）。</span></li><li id=\"u65a734e7\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">子域名间</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（如 a.taobao.com 和 b.taobao.com）：可以通过设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Domain=.主域名.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 实现共享。</span></li><li id=\"ufd58bcc1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">同一应用不同路径</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：默认可以共享（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Path=/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u05a5578d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">现代最佳实践</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：如果是完全跨域的场景（不同主域名），现在更推荐使用 Token（如 JWT）放在 Authorization Header 中进行认证，而不是依赖 Cookie 共享。这样可以避免第三方 Cookie 限制带来的复杂性和兼容性问题。</span></li></ul></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"uf0d5dde2\" id=\"uf0d5dde2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubf8cd238\" id=\"ubf8cd238\">简短的回答是：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6f595a64\" id=\"u6f595a64\">Cookie 可以在</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u39bda39d\" id=\"u39bda39d\">主域名相同但子域名不同</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u930dd311\" id=\"u930dd311\">的情况下共享，但无法在</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u866860fc\" id=\"u866860fc\">完全不同</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0113269b\" id=\"u0113269b\">的主域名之间直接共享。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u39e1be3c\" id=\"u39e1be3c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf8999d13\" id=\"uf8999d13\">如果想实现跨域共享，需要满足一些严格的条件，并且随着浏览器隐私策略的升级，现在的限制越来越多。下面分情况说明：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22aUF0N%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"BbSJ3\" id=\"BbSJ3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab99c555\" id=\"uab99c555\">1. 同主域下的共享（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u73c407b6\" id=\"u73c407b6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubab8a58c\" id=\"ubab8a58c\">a.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0b530532\" id=\"u0b530532\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua9b5dc34\" id=\"ua9b5dc34\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5ed42148\" id=\"u5ed42148\">b.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9f9cb11a\" id=\"u9f9cb11a\">）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u3e6a0f90\" id=\"u3e6a0f90\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue62dbbf1\" id=\"ue62dbbf1\">这是最常见的跨子域共享场景。核心是通过设置 Cookie 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uec6ccdc7\" id=\"uec6ccdc7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub486e3cf\" id=\"ub486e3cf\">Domain</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u04c3b005\" id=\"u04c3b005\"> 属性实现。</span></p><ul list=\"u1e068298\"><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"uf8fb7733\" id=\"uf8fb7733\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23c5e25b\" id=\"u23c5e25b\">实现方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1735fbb3\" id=\"u1735fbb3\">：在设置 Cookie 时，将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8ce68773\" id=\"u8ce68773\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6983ea57\" id=\"u6983ea57\">Domain</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf265e82\" id=\"ucf265e82\"> 属性设置为根域名（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc7c6c9c7\" id=\"uc7c6c9c7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4ae6006\" id=\"ua4ae6006\">.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue965e72d\" id=\"ue965e72d\">，注意开头的点）。这样，该 Cookie 就会被发送到 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud6bf4afe\" id=\"ud6bf4afe\"><span data-lake-id=\"u264c0b9c\" id=\"u264c0b9c\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc4c22591\" id=\"uc4c22591\"> 下的所有子域名（包括 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u657e7c14\" id=\"u657e7c14\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4f12ef87\" id=\"u4f12ef87\">a.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3b83e2cb\" id=\"u3b83e2cb\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"ua5fc7d64\" id=\"ua5fc7d64\"><span data-lake-id=\"uef448692\" id=\"uef448692\">b.example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ubb20ab06\" id=\"ubb20ab06\"> 以及 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u609b6bb3\" id=\"u609b6bb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1640209f\" id=\"u1640209f\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u431ed253\" id=\"u431ed253\"> 本身）。</span></li><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"u9ffb2d93\" id=\"u9ffb2d93\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6611baab\" id=\"u6611baab\">示例</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9e46ad1d\" id=\"u9e46ad1d\">：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88Node.js%20Express%EF%BC%89%5Cnres.cookie('sessionId'%2C%20'value'%2C%20%7B%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20domain%3A%20'.example.com'%2C%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%B9%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%5Cn%20%20%20%20path%3A%20'%2F'%2C%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20httpOnly%3A%20true%20%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22zxDcb%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u1e068298\" start=\"3\"><li fid=\"u4d551805\" data-lake-id=\"ud20f1abd\" id=\"ud20f1abd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u21658819\" id=\"u21658819\">注意</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0888b374\" id=\"u0888b374\">：这种方式仅限于共享同一主域名的不同子域，对于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7395a142\" id=\"u7395a142\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc4dc7fd\" id=\"ufc4dc7fd\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf3674ccd\" id=\"uf3674ccd\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5ad6cb78\" id=\"u5ad6cb78\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue6db558f\" id=\"ue6db558f\">baidu.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub29f8ea1\" id=\"ub29f8ea1\"> 这种情况无效。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"Azr5B\" id=\"Azr5B\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0b49964a\" id=\"u0b49964a\">2. 完全跨域共享（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u23f04cec\" id=\"u23f04cec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56295c10\" id=\"u56295c10\">example.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2331f2a1\" id=\"u2331f2a1\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ube31707c\" id=\"ube31707c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4ebfc05b\" id=\"u4ebfc05b\">api.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue50b10fa\" id=\"ue50b10fa\">）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uf44fc91e\" id=\"uf44fc91e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u783c9496\" id=\"u783c9496\">如果是两个完全不同主域名的网站（例如前端在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ued206ba6\" id=\"ued206ba6\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf52998d8\" id=\"uf52998d8\">a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u66586576\" id=\"u66586576\">，后端在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0c04754e\" id=\"u0c04754e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56debe2c\" id=\"u56debe2c\">b.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u99b144a8\" id=\"u99b144a8\">），需要借助 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3aa4aa6f\" id=\"u3aa4aa6f\">CORS（跨域资源共享）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udbcf3aac\" id=\"udbcf3aac\"> 机制，并配合 Cookie 的现代属性设置。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc802bcfc\" id=\"uc802bcfc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u64066611\" id=\"u64066611\">这需要</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a363d21\" id=\"u6a363d21\">前后端同时配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98438996\" id=\"u98438996\">才能生效：</span></p><ul list=\"uad007ee2\"><li fid=\"ud25e9cb7\" data-lake-id=\"u71cfa077\" id=\"u71cfa077\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub6e99954\" id=\"ub6e99954\">后端必须配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0d1d8068\" id=\"u0d1d8068\">：</span></li></ul><ol list=\"uad007ee2\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"u3b1e3249\" id=\"u3b1e3249\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9dbf3e7e\" id=\"u9dbf3e7e\">设置明确的允许源</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u78c5dda1\" id=\"u78c5dda1\">：响应头 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8c187a50\" id=\"u8c187a50\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5490f5ed\" id=\"u5490f5ed\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u29f1a825\" id=\"u29f1a825\"> 不能是通配符 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3f09ea4d\" id=\"u3f09ea4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3a1824c\" id=\"ud3a1824c\">*</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5faafb50\" id=\"u5faafb50\">，必须是具体的域名（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1f5c051b\" id=\"u1f5c051b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0b80fda4\" id=\"u0b80fda4\">https://a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf07b9ce0\" id=\"uf07b9ce0\">）。</span></li><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"ue40c6779\" id=\"ue40c6779\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u316ed220\" id=\"u316ed220\">允许携带凭证</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uce6c2b3a\" id=\"uce6c2b3a\">：设置响应头 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3a14855c\" id=\"u3a14855c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uac149f40\" id=\"uac149f40\">Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2211011e\" id=\"u2211011e\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u8d6e3b65\" data-lake-id=\"u57594139\" id=\"u57594139\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u25530482\" id=\"u25530482\">Cookie 属性配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub957f659\" id=\"ub957f659\">：必须设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf14c4879\" id=\"uf14c4879\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue52010fa\" id=\"ue52010fa\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2568d94c\" id=\"u2568d94c\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua21d4fa9\" id=\"ua21d4fa9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u305a175e\" id=\"u305a175e\">Secure</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9595f154\" id=\"u9595f154\">。因为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ucf4d1ebc\" id=\"ucf4d1ebc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d6ffb91\" id=\"u6d6ffb91\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u031263b3\" id=\"u031263b3\"> 要求 Cookie 必须在安全上下文（HTTPS）中才能发送。</span></li></ol><ul list=\"uad007ee2\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"ud25e9cb7\" data-lake-id=\"u88772fbc\" id=\"u88772fbc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u51d03aac\" id=\"u51d03aac\">前端必须配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u68da4b5b\" id=\"u68da4b5b\">：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%20(%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20fetch)%5Cnfetch('https%3A%2F%2Fapi.com%2Fdata'%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20method%3A%20'GET'%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20credentials%3A%20'include'%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%90%BA%E5%B8%A6%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%20Cookie%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22xw3Yv%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"uad007ee2\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u5b58eda0\" data-lake-id=\"ub4571233\" id=\"ub4571233\"><span data-lake-id=\"u937bc4b1\" id=\"u937bc4b1\">在发送请求时，显式设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf3015264\" id=\"uf3015264\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3beb248d\" id=\"u3beb248d\">withCredentials</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u602ba370\" id=\"u602ba370\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uab7356d5\" id=\"uab7356d5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6155b0e5\" id=\"u6155b0e5\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud66a3529\" id=\"ud66a3529\">（XHR）或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uedb8f6a2\" id=\"uedb8f6a2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uadc11745\" id=\"uadc11745\">credentials: 'include'</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua78fb9e5\" id=\"ua78fb9e5\">（Fetch API）。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"eLzVk\" id=\"eLzVk\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0a58ea6d\" id=\"u0a58ea6d\">3. 现代浏览器的限制</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u958a006a\" id=\"u958a006a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u19e553b6\" id=\"u19e553b6\">即使上述代码配置正确，现在实现跨域共享 Cookie 也比以前更难，主要是出于隐私保护：</span></p><ul list=\"u333f4b65\"><li fid=\"ub58f14b8\" data-lake-id=\"u71d5ca8c\" id=\"u71d5ca8c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued0e2feb\" id=\"ued0e2feb\">第三方 Cookie 限制</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u621599fe\" id=\"u621599fe\">：许多现代浏览器（如 Safari 的 ITP、Chrome 逐步推行的“隐私沙盒”）默认开始限制或完全阻止第三方 Cookie。当你访问 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8e5bc991\" id=\"u8e5bc991\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5921053d\" id=\"u5921053d\">a.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1e934762\" id=\"u1e934762\"> 时，向 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u40c9bfea\" id=\"u40c9bfea\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud445d585\" id=\"ud445d585\">b.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2288f1a9\" id=\"u2288f1a9\"> 发送请求携带的 Cookie 被视为“第三方 Cookie”，可能会被浏览器丢弃。</span></li><li fid=\"ub58f14b8\" data-lake-id=\"u9d257e06\" id=\"u9d257e06\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u10f7fae0\" id=\"u10f7fae0\">状态分区</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u621320b8\" id=\"u621320b8\">：Firefox 等浏览器引入了“状态分区”机制。即使你设置了 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1ac9801b\" id=\"u1ac9801b\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc5858745\" id=\"uc5858745\">SameSite=None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufe4d0118\" id=\"ufe4d0118\">，浏览器也可能根据顶级域名对存储进行分区，使得在不同顶级网站下嵌入的同一第三方无法共享之前的 Cookie。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"mM3o0\" id=\"mM3o0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufef02e18\" id=\"ufef02e18\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"u70914b7e\"><li fid=\"u04fb7b01\" data-lake-id=\"ua8b19626\" id=\"ua8b19626\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf68dc187\" id=\"uf68dc187\">共享规则</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucf9eb4b4\" id=\"ucf9eb4b4\">：</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u70914b7e\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"u80b4e3a1\" id=\"u80b4e3a1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaa23b60d\" id=\"uaa23b60d\">完全跨主域</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6319d117\" id=\"u6319d117\">（如 a.com 和 b.com）：默认</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u81be7e1e\" id=\"u81be7e1e\">不能</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua85e6749\" id=\"ua85e6749\">直接共享，需借助复杂的 CORS 配置和 SameSite=None（但受浏览器第三方 Cookie 策略影响，越来越难）。</span></li><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"u65a734e7\" id=\"u65a734e7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaffe5fef\" id=\"uaffe5fef\">子域名间</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uadc73ee1\" id=\"uadc73ee1\">（如 a.taobao.com 和 b.taobao.com）：可以通过设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc89c0bb3\" id=\"uc89c0bb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8ad82c67\" id=\"u8ad82c67\">Domain=.主域名.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2faf4da6\" id=\"u2faf4da6\"> 实现共享。</span></li><li fid=\"uecd946a5\" data-lake-id=\"ufd58bcc1\" id=\"ufd58bcc1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub824c2cb\" id=\"ub824c2cb\">同一应用不同路径</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3cd95a93\" id=\"u3cd95a93\">：默认可以共享（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u4890a34f\" id=\"u4890a34f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u727b6bc4\" id=\"u727b6bc4\">Path=/</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u283fff67\" id=\"u283fff67\">）。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u70914b7e\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"u04fb7b01\" data-lake-id=\"u05a5578d\" id=\"u05a5578d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2e46b501\" id=\"u2e46b501\">现代最佳实践</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf1e062a2\" id=\"uf1e062a2\">：如果是完全跨域的场景（不同主域名），现在更推荐使用 Token（如 JWT）放在 Authorization Header 中进行认证，而不是依赖 Cookie 共享。这样可以避免第三方 Cookie 限制带来的复杂性和兼容性问题。</span></li></ul>","word_count":920,"slug":"ri8scw04apvl07wk","type":"Doc","title":"cookie 可以实现在不同域名下共享吗？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"简短的回答是：Cookie 可以在主域名相同但子域名不同的情况下共享，但无法在完全不同的主域名之间直接共享。如果想实现跨域共享，需要满足一些严格的条件，并且随着浏览器隐私策略的升级，现在的限制越来越多。下面分情况说明：1. 同主域下的共享（如 a.example.com 和 b.example...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"hr\":1,\"codeblock\":2}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-26T07:23:17.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-26T07:28:41.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-26T07:28:41.499Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-26T07:28:41.000Z","id":257992945},"doc_digest":"8T5kK6cAG7VA48LOxDGFBT_o9u0"}